@startuml
title ATM State Machine for Withdrawal

[*] --> SelectAmount

state "SelectAmount"
state VerifyTransaction
state RejectedAmount
state DispenseCash
state PrintReceipt
state ReturnCard
state LoggedOut

SelectAmount --> VerifyTransaction : amount selected
VerifyTransaction --> DispenseCash : verify transaction approved
VerifyTransaction --> RejectedAmount : verify transaction rejected

RejectedAmount --> SelectAmount : re-enter amount
DispenseCash --> PrintReceipt : cash dispensed
PrintReceipt --> ReturnCard : print receipt, return card
LoggedOut --> [*] : user logged out
@enduml
